<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Her ex-fiancé Reece Hawkins has just announced that he's expecting a baby with his model partner, London Goheen. </p>

<p>And now Tammy Hembrow has revealed how she got over their breakup, after they split back in 2018.</p>

<p>Speaking on her podcast, Hanging With The Hembrows, the 26-year-old said that she focused on herself and their children while nursing a broken heart. </p>

<p>'It just takes time': Tammy Hembrow revealed on her podcast this week how she got over her breakup with ex-fiancé Reece Hawkins</p>

<p>'Reece was younger than me, he was in the grade below me at school,' Tammy began, as she reflected on their relationship.</p>

<p>She went on to say that 'age is just a number,' before being quizzed by her sisters Amy, Emilee and Starlette about how she got through their split. </p>

<p>'Just like trying to have a positive mindset, keeping busy and doing things you enjoy doing,' Tammy said. </p>

<p>Priorities: The 26-year-old said that she focused on herself and their children while nursing a broken heart. Pictured with son Wolf</p>

<p>She added: 'Focusing on yourself, work and kids, that's all the stuff that helped me.'</p>

<p>Tammy also said during the podcast, which was giving Starlette tips on how to get through life in your twenties, that getting over a breakup 'takes time.'</p>

<p>'It just takes time. Time heals all wounds, you can't expect it to be over in a day,' Tammy said. </p>

<p>She added: 'Take it day by day and focus on the present moment.'</p>

<p>Tammy and Reece split in 2018 after five years of dating. </p>

<p>Moving on: 'It just takes time. Time heals all wounds, you can't expect it to be over in a day,' Tammy said</p>

<p>They share son Wolf, five, and daughter Saskia, four, together. </p>

<p>Last Wednesday, Reece and new fiancée London Goheen announced that they are expecting their first child together. </p>

<p>The announcement came just weeks after they got engaged.</p>

<p>American model London, 22, made the announcement on Instagram, by sharing a sweet image of herself kissing influencer Reece, 25. </p>

<p>Baby joy: Last Wednesday, Reece and new fiancée London Goheen announced that they are expecting their first child together</p>

<p>'Been busy growing a BABY in my belly with this one wbu?' London captioned the image. </p>

<p>Reece also shared similar images of the pair, calling London his 'Baby Momma' and the 'love of my life.'</p>

<p>'Baby Momma alert. Having a baby with the love of my life and my best friend,' he wrote.</p>

<p>She was recently slammed for charging fans $14.99 to see baby bump pics on OnlyFans. </p>

<p>The couple have been dating since mid-2018, getting together shortly after his split with Tammy. </p>

